{"tid":2473373,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"呢度有無人都睇緊《天國稅》(2) 作品資訊整合PO","createTime":"2021-04-03T07:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T14:30:03.000Z","uid":51088,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d92334ec621c472f0d22430e715015f5579bf66","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"上一個PO : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/236856\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/236856</a><br />\n<br />\n發覺上一個PO啲資訊太散，搞無乜人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以今個PO整合返。<br />\n<br />\n《天國稅》<br />\n在這個時代，大家都很努力賺錢。<br />\n因為只要有錢，就能夠上天國。<br />\n<img src=\"https://d3tdq0klf4qqp.cloudfront.net/images/books/84/59/8459682805fd45873428ba8.51134960-89723.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd3tdq0klf4qqp.cloudfront.net%2Fimages%2Fbooks%2F84%2F59%2F8459682805fd45873428ba8.51134960-89723.jpeg&h=567f4a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>連載地方</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作者IG：<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/hei_7537/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhei_7537%2F&d=k77hOMsO7CBmOnyTOgf%2B4RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=0005afb3\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/hei_7537/</a><br />\nPENANA（最新集）：<a href=\"http://www.penana.com/story/72118/天國税p&lambda;r&lambda;dis&xi;-t&lambda;x/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F72118%2F%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%8B%E7%A8%8Ep%CE%BBr%CE%BBdis%CE%BE-t%CE%BBx%2Ftoc&d=k77hOMsO7CBmOnyTOgf%2B4RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=a2b0f772\" target=\"_blank\">www.penana.com/story/72118/天國税p&lambda;r&lambda;dis&xi;-t&lambda;x/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>作品名言集：</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出自第八集尾<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdFRvKKDopqyLtGgSXSNyjdjNeT1Fk6GaX4bQMgctD8pw?filename=2tfDMVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tfDMVk.png&h=5ea58149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出自第五集尾<br />\n<img src=\"https://d3tdq0klf4qqp.cloudfront.net/images/content/89723/2996761585fded11ea8abb1.26064790-89723.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd3tdq0klf4qqp.cloudfront.net%2Fimages%2Fcontent%2F89723%2F2996761585fded11ea8abb1.26064790-89723.jpeg&h=15668d3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>點解要睇？</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係香港人就會明呢個故想講乜。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>作者動向</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整sticker 巧打意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQxbKHCaPnKs42wN9LmWTrQyNoqkWUJmZmQxtn9mrGR3u?filename=GqNmCMv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqNmCMv.png&h=19483bc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時會送poster （有訂咗佢嘅話） <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmamt7UN2ZCGzEHUuSmbnqzwfPSCJtQY28BARfAhHdSSfs?filename=F3g26Fw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF3g26Fw.png&h=69d7e641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>你問我係咪打手？ </strong><br />\n係，歡迎打鳩我，香港漫畫再唔推就無，而且真係好睇，你屌鳩我都無用。唔中意就負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88388d5b0da6ac6903c08cf92c507482029478c0","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T07:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSMGt4bTUcgxrKkLWSFGA4qN5s26Aiar1uCc2XcNCVdVV?filename=QxAZ8U9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxAZ8U9.png&h=9a64c958&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n本PＯ兼漫畫吉詳物，鳩叫雀（我自己改，唔知作者係咪呢個名）"},{"pid":"bb212c4ef0eedb6ad741a49fcaf231e44fe21a06","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVmg6v3hpEjwJJsXRUJWdpQHtVkCQK3mahFreJfKiK6jA?filename=zAx9MH3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAx9MH3.png&h=044d6634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連隔離故台，勁出名嘅三哥都課金讚好<br />\n唔課金都畀ＬＩＫＥ Ｇ持吓喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95048659e25e842d2cb4ab1fdaf52dd4d748d57a","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcc4814ba2f8dcad5efb1b8ef2f041f9eb614250","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25a0b9bb160471bd92218933d0e67227b225e72d","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T08:08:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"222dce7ff5416819b4b9c9638ad9ab00fb96a835","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T08:10:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c536f374726e436217ac501e5b8ddb17009a1525","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T08:21:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba163c16b992e167f7e840274e702cb64e2a61df","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T08:42:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"199571077612900d41863b6d47741731a3dfe822","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T09:56:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aad6a84d8ca901b087d0604c219394e2bd52566c","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8774af47ba0c6d03748ad99b8ce8cb2f9378a086","tid":2473373,"uid":51088,"like":0,"d